rComments: It felt like the students were running the class instead of her, with her "discussion space" BS. She gave crazy large amounts of readings. I'm sorry but I'm not memorizing the entire Canadian Health Act for an exam. Super vague with what we should be studying. If I could give her 0/5 I would. Her class felt like I was throwing darts into the dark

Pre records slide shows of her reading the slides like we are illiterate with almost no explanations. Has "classes" which are just discussions and she does no teaching at all in these sessions. Tells you to do all readings but the only thing that is relevant for exams is the slides so don't waste your time reading the readings she gives.
